  "texts": [
    "C. Real-world Application and DeploymentIn practical terms, the deployment of these AI models in real-world spam detection systems requires careful consideration of their operational contexts.",
    "ChatGPT-4's balanced approach makes it an attractive option for platforms that prioritize user experience and the minimization of false positives.",
    "On the other hand, Google Gemini's approach could be more suited to environments where the cost of missing spam emails is high, such as in financial or secure communication platforms.",
    "The choice between these models thus hinges on the specific needs and priorities of the deployment environment, including factors such as user base characteristics, communication criticality, and acceptable risk levels of false positives and negatives.",
    "D. Limitations of This StudyThis study, while providing valuable insights, is not without its limitations."
  ]
}